<ptxt>
DTC detecting condition
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Trouble area
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</thead>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
<emph>
P0340: Camshaft Position Sensor “A” Circuit
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Any of the following conditions is met.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
CMP sensor signal is not inputted while CKP sensor signal is being inputted.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
CMP sensor signal pattern is not equal to the expected pattern.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<ptxt>
(3 D/C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
CMP sensor and/or its circuit
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Signal rotor
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
ECM
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</servinfosub>
